### MessageController HTTP Requests

# 1. Send Message
POST http://localhost:8080/api/messages
Authorization: Bearer <token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Hello group!",
  "groupId": 1
}

###

# 2. Get Conversations
GET http://localhost:8080/api/messages/conversations
Authorization: Bearer <token>

###

# 3. Get Conversation Messages
GET http://localhost:8080/api/messages/conversations/1
Authorization: Bearer <token>

###

# 4. Get Unread Messages
GET http://localhost:8080/api/messages/unread
Authorization: Bearer <token>

###

# 5. Get Unread Message Count
GET http://localhost:8080/api/messages/unread/count
Authorization: Bearer <token>

###

# 6. Mark Message as Read
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/messages/1/read
Authorization: Bearer <token> 